<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 21:12:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>CIA现在说Covid-19“更有可能”来自实验室</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/cia-now-says-covid-19-more-likely-have-come-lab-2025-01-25/</link><description>一位机构发言人周六表示，中央情报机构评估了Covid-19的大流行“更有可能”从实验室而不是大自然中出现。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 19:23:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/cia-now-says-covid-19-more-likely-have-come-lab-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>上海用狗的晚餐庆祝农历新年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-celebrates-lunar-new-year-with-dogs-dinner-2025-01-25/</link><description>Yakult热情地咬了一口，在舔嘴唇之前，在他面前咬了一口镀鸡肉和生菜。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 13:47:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-celebrates-lunar-new-year-with-dogs-dinner-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾在中国的“骚扰”之后暂停了南中国海调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-harassing-its-fisheries-boats-south-china-sea-2025-01-25/</link><description>菲律宾周六表示，在其两艘渔业船面临“骚扰”和中国海岸警卫队和海军的侵略性行为之后，它已暂停了在南中国海进行的一项科学调查。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 02:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-harassing-its-fisheries-boats-south-china-sea-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>英国高级议员说，消费者和投资者希望在中国棉花上真相</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/senior-uk-lawmaker-says-consumers-investors-want-truth-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</link><description>英国议会委员会主席周五表示，英国消费者和投资者希望对中国新疆省的棉花产品是否由英国的在线快速时尚零售商Shein出售。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/senior-uk-lawmaker-says-consumers-investors-want-truth-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>王告诉卢比奥领导者有我们 - 中国领带的基调和方向</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-top-diplomat-rubio-chinas-wang-speak-first-phone-call-china-says-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国外交部长王伊周五与新美国国务卿马可·卢比奥（Marco Rubio）交谈，北京表示，他告诉已知的中国鹰，美国领导人的方向和基调是由他们的领导人建立的，他希望卢比奥扮演着建设性的角色为了两国人民的利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:36:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-top-diplomat-rubio-chinas-wang-speak-first-phone-call-china-says-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国说，菲律宾在有争议的环礁向军舰发送了规定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-sent-provisions-warship-disputed-atoll-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国海岸警卫队周五表示，菲律宾派出了一艘民用船只，在第二托马斯·肖尔（Thomas Shoal）“非法扎根”的军舰上，这是南中国海的一个有争议的环礁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 15:25:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-sent-provisions-warship-disputed-atoll-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>Shein告诉英国议员，它不允许中国棉花在我们出售的产品中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-details-cotton-sourcing-policy-written-evidence-uk-lawmakers-2025-01-24/</link><description>该公司周五表示，在线快速时尚零售商Shein要求其合同制造商仅从包括中国在内的批准地区采购棉花，用于其在美国出售的产品，最大的市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:31:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-details-cotton-sourcing-policy-written-evidence-uk-lawmakers-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>文字显示，美国立法者寻求对香港的权利制裁。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmakers-seek-rights-sanctions-over-hong-kong-text-shows-2025-01-24/</link><description>根据路透社的一份法案，共和党和民主党立法者将在周五提出一项法案，要求特朗普政府审查是否应因侵犯人权行为而批准香港官员。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:05:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmakers-seek-rights-sanctions-over-hong-kong-text-shows-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：律师说，他说他为中国监视了，赌博大亨在泰国监狱虐待。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/gambling-tycoon-abused-thai-jail-after-saying-he-spied-china-lawyers-say-2025-01-24/</link><description>他的律师告诉国际刑警组织，一名被判入狱的赌博大亨在泰国监狱中战斗，在泰国监狱中获得了“不人道的待遇”，他说他们担心他的一生。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/gambling-tycoon-abused-thai-jail-after-saying-he-spied-china-lawyers-say-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>泰国和中国建立协调中心，以打击骗局电话网络</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-set-up-coordination-centre-combat-scam-call-networks-2025-01-24/</link><description>泰国和中国将共同努力，打击泰国与缅甸和柬埔寨沿泰国边境的非法呼叫中心的快速发展网络，通常由被贩运的工人组成，旨在欺骗电话和在线骗局。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:41:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-set-up-coordination-centre-combat-scam-call-networks-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国2024财政收入增长萎缩，非税收收入跳跃</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-2024-fiscal-revenue-grows-13-down-64-year-earlier-2025-01-24/</link><description>财政部的数据周五显示，中国在2024年的财政收入比去年同期增长了1.3％，这是由于2023年的6.4％增长，因为旷日持久的房地产市场下跌，而国内需求放缓则对经济产生了压力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:16:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-2024-fiscal-revenue-grows-13-down-64-year-earlier-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国男子因刺伤日本男孩而被判处死刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/alleged-killer-japanese-schoolboy-goes-trial-china-say-japans-foreign-ministry-2025-01-24/</link><description>日本凯多通讯社周五说，一个中国法院因在南部城市深圳的一名日本男孩的致命刺伤而判处死刑，周五说，日本驻中国大使肯吉·卡纳苏吉（Kenji Kanasugi）说。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 08:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/alleged-killer-japanese-schoolboy-goes-trial-china-say-japans-foreign-ministry-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>在担心经济的情况下，中国新年新年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-readies-lunar-new-year-amid-worries-about-economy-2025-01-24/</link><description>周五，旅行者挤满了火车站和机场，抓着大型的行李箱和礼物，例如盒子的水果，他们加入数百万中国人返回家乡，与家人一起庆祝月球新年节。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 07:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-readies-lunar-new-year-amid-worries-about-economy-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国刺激计划将2024年的消费增长提高了1 pct点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-stimulus-scheme-lifted-2024-consumption-growth-by-1-pct-point-2025-01-24/</link><description>副商务部长尚昂·齐普（Sheng Qiuping）周五表示，中国对消费品交易的刺激计划使去年的消费增长增长了1个百分点以上。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 06:10:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-stimulus-scheme-lifted-2024-consumption-growth-by-1-pct-point-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>假期前，中国主要的港口被拥堵击中，特朗普关税威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/major-chinese-port-hit-by-congestion-ahead-holiday-trump-tariff-threat-2025-01-24/</link><description>出口商本周从深圳的Yantian港口（全球最大的集装箱港口之一）登上了装载和运输货物，在一个八天的农历新年假期之前，并在美国对中国商品的关税可能浪费之前。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 05:42:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/major-chinese-port-hit-by-congestion-ahead-holiday-trump-tariff-threat-2025-01-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>